
// This code snippet uses an [if] statement to check if the [name] node within the current [dp] node equals "wheel". If true, it sets the [status] node within the same [dp] node to "urgent restock". The [if] condition evaluates the [name] node, and if it matches, the [.lambda] block updates the [status] node.
if
   eq:x:@.dp/#/*/name
      .:wheel
   .lambda
      set-value:x:@.dp/#/*/status
         .:urgent restock
